rawContent:
I often try to find ways to justify my #depression when it happens, as if people HAVE to justify feeling their negative feelings.

I wouldn’t expect that from anyone else; why do I expect it from myself?

So why the fuck is it so hard for me to accept my depression?

#bipolarclub
